<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <title>관리자 페이지 - 2040 SHOP</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
        <h1>👮‍♂️ 관리자 주문 관리 시스템</h1>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark">쇼핑몰 메인으로</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
            <table class="table table-hover align-middle text-center">
                <thead class="table-dark">
                <tr>
                    <th>주문번호</th>
                    <th>구매자</th>
                    <th>상품명</th>
                    <th>현재 상태</th>
                    <th>상태 변경 (관리)</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {{#orders}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{id}}</td>
                        <td>{{member.name}}</td>
                        <td>{{item.name}}</td>
                        <td>
                            <span class="badge bg-secondary">{{status}}</span>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            <div class="btn-group" role="group">
                                <form action="/admin/order/status" method="post" class="d-inline">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="orderId" value="{{id}}">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="status" value="SHIPPING">
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm me-1">🚚 배송 시작</button>
                                </form>

                                <form action="/admin/order/status" method="post" class="d-inline">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="orderId" value="{{id}}">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="status" value="DELIVERED">
                                    <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm">✅ 배송 완료</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                {{/orders}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>